message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with signal processing and audio analysis. cs.CV is also likely as it deals with computer vision and image analysis, which can be applied to spectrograms and other visual representations of audio signals. cs.LG is another possibility as it deals with machine learning, which is a key component of the proposed approach. cs.CL is also possible as it deals with natural language processing, which can be applied to speech recognition and transcription. cs.MM is less likely but still possible as it deals with multimedia systems, which can include audio analysis and classification.
